trans-unit.source: ⚠︎ UIGF v2.3 (and earlier) JSON files & UIGF v2.2 Excel Spreadsheets are exported without timezone information, and the apps used for generating these files may have individual behaviors in handling timezone information. - For such files generated by Snap Hutao (v1.7.16_2023-11-10 and earlier) in these deprecated formats, please set the fallback time zone to UTC+0. - For such files generated by Xunkong (v1.4.4_2024-04-24) in these deprecated formats, please set the fallback time zone to the server time zone. Xunkong provided no UIGF v2.4 support and they introduced the gacha timezone support with UIGF v3.0 support starts from v1.5.0 update on 2024-09-21. - For such files generated by Teyvat Helper (YShelper), please set the fallback time to the device time where this file was generated and exported by Teyvat Helper.
trans-unit.target: ⚠︎ Ang mga JSON file ng UIGF v2.3 (at mas naunang bersyon) at Excel Spreadsheets ng UIGF v2.2 ay ine-export nang walang impormasyong time zone, at ang mga app na ginamit para sa pagbuo ng mga file na ito ay maaaring may kanya-kanyang pag-uugali sa paghawak ng impormasyon sa time zone. - Para sa mga file na tulad nito na nabuo ng Snap Hutao (v1.7.16_2023-11-10 at mas naunang bersyon) sa mga format na hindi na ginagamit, mangyaring itakda ang fallback time zone sa UTC+0. - Para sa mga file na tulad nito na nabuo ng Xunkong (v1.4.4_2024-04-24) sa mga format na hindi na ginagamit, mangyaring itakda ang fallback time zone sa server time zone. Walang ibinigay na suporta sa UIGF v2.4 si Xunkong at nagpakilala sila ng suporta sa gacha timezone sa UIGF v3.0 simula sa pag-update ng v1.5.0 noong 2024-09-21. - Para sa mga file na tulad nito na nabuo ng Teyvat Helper (YShelper), mangyaring itakda ang fallback time sa time ng device kung saan nilikha at ine-export ng Teyvat Helper ang file na ito.

trans-unit.source: SRGF v1.0, established by the UIGF committee, is an exchangeable format for gacha records of Star Rail, a game produced by Cognosphere and MiHoYo. trans-unit.source: Due to occasional server-side accidents, the game server may return duplicated gacha entries with incorrect transaction IDs, polluting the local database. If the bleaching mode is enabled, this app will use the latest fetch results as the trust source of correct transaction IDs and remove the incorrect entries on the local side, but this can be deceived by the polluted data from the game server. Nevertheless, as long as a game version deprecates, all gacha records during its operation period will become static and trustable.
trans-unit.target: Dahil sa mga hindi inaasahang insidente sa server, maaaring magbalik ang game server ng mga dobleng gacha entry na may maling transaction ID, na nagdudulot ng polusyon sa lokal na database. Kung naka-enable ang bleaching mode, gagamitin ng app na ito ang pinakabagong resulta ng pagkuha bilang mapagkakatiwalaang pinagmulan ng tamang transaction ID at aalisin ang maling entry, ngunit maaaring malinlang ng kontaminadong data mula sa game server. Gayunpaman, kapag ang isang game version ay nag-expire, lahat ng gacha record mula sa operasyon nito ay magiging static at mapagkakatiwalaan.

trans-unit.source:
New UI language settings of an app on macOS / iOS always require the app to restart to make sure the new language setting becomes effective to it. Even if the user manually change this through System Settings, user will still be prompted the necessity of restarting the app, and it will be not this app but the macOS / iOS who prompts it.
We make this language switcher here to save users some seconds. This design is extremely ADHD-friendly since ADHD patients are likely to forgot what they are about to do while flipping among nested pages in iOS / macOS System Settings.
This app will quit after you confirm this message.
trans-unit.target:
Ang mga bagong setting ng wika para sa UI ng isang app sa macOS / iOS ay palaging nangangailangan na i-restart ang app upang matiyak na magiging epektibo ang bagong setting ng wika. Kahit na mano-mano itong baguhin ng gumagamit sa pamamagitan ng System Settings, ipapaalala pa rin sa gumagamit ang pangangailangan ng pag-restart ng app, at hindi ang app na ito kundi ang macOS / iOS ang magpo-prompt nito.
Ginawa namin ang language switcher na ito upang makatipid ng ilang segundo para sa mga gumagamit. Ang disenyo na ito ay napaka-ADHD-friendly sapagkat ang mga may ADHD ay madalas nakakalimutan ang gagawin habang naglilipat-lipat sa mga naka-nest na pahina sa System Settings ng iOS / macOS.
Ang app na ito ay magsasara pagkatapos mong kumpirmahin ang mensaheng ito.

trans-unit.source: To get resin and other data from HoYoLAB / Miyoushe, UID and login cookie of your account is needed. trans-unit.source: To ensure you feel safe with this, here’s how it works: Your password input is protected by macOS built-in SecureEventInputAPI (or its equivalent on iOS), and then it will be directly handled by HoYoLAB login webpage. This is the nature of how WKWebView gets designed by Apple. Nobody else can interfere / intercept this process, nor this app. You can see that you cannot switch to 3rd-party input methods while the password is receiving inputs from the user.
trans-unit.target: Para masiguro mong ligtas ka rito, ganito ito gumagana: Ang iyong input ng password ay pinoprotektahan ng macOS built-in SecureEventInputAPI (o katumbas nito sa iOS), at pagkatapos ay direktang pinanghahawakan ng HoYoLAB login webpage. Ito ang likas na disenyo ng WKWebView ng Apple. Walang sinumang maaaring makialam/makahadlang sa prosesong ito, maging ang app na ito. Makikita mong hindi ka makakalipat sa 3rd-party input methods habang ang password ay tumatanggap ng input mula sa gumagamit.

trans-unit.source: This option is extremely helpful to let the server know that you are really using your HoYoLAB / Miyoushe account on your own devices. Individual logins per UID for each game and each game-server may let the HoYoLAB / Miyoushe account server misunderstood how many device this HoYoLAB / Miyoushe account gets logged into, leading to earlier expiration of your cookies. If profile duplication happens during this process, then the existing profile will be updated instead with new cookie, the latest device fingerprint, and the latest device ID instead.

Kung mangyari ang pag-duplicate ng profile sa prosesong ito, ang kasalukuyang profile ay maa-update sa halip gamit ang bagong cookie, ang pinakabagong fingerprint ng device, at ang pinakabagong ID ng device.
